# Version Bump When Updating Slide Content

Whenever you edit [cards-data.js](cards-data.js) (slide content, bullets, paragraphs, resources, or structure), also increment the version number shown in the nav.

- **Where:** [index.html](index.html) — the `<span class="version">vN</span>` in the nav (e.g. `v10` → `v11`).
- **When:** Same commit or change set as the cards-data.js edit.

This keeps the displayed version in sync with slide content changes.
